{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "a8f45550-1a47-4f5b-a009-40b347cf0cdd",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Atlantean Dragoons",
      "effect": "All your Level 3 or lower Sea Serpent monsters can attack directly. If this card is sent to the GY to activate a WATER monster's effect: Add 1 Sea Serpent monster from your Deck to your hand, except \"Atlantean Dragoons\"."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Cavalerie Dragon de l'Atlantide",
      "effect": "Tous vos monstres Serpent de Mer de max. Niveau 3 peuvent attaquer directement. Si cette carte est envoy\u00e9e au Cimeti\u00e8re pour activer un effet de monstre EAU : ajoutez 1 monstre Serpent de Mer (\"Cavalerie Dragon de l'Atlantide\" exclu) depuis votre Deck \u00e0 votre main."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Atlantische Dragoner",
      "effect": "Alle deine Seeschlange-Monster der Stufe 3 oder niedriger k\u00f6nnen direkt angreifen. Falls diese Karte auf den Friedhof gelegt wird, um den Effekt eines WASSER Monsters zu aktivieren: F\u00fcge deiner Hand 1 Seeschlange-Monster von deinem Deck hinzu, au\u00dfer \u201eAtlantische Dragoner\u201c."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Dragoni Atlantici",
      "effect": "Tutti i tuoi mostri Serpente Marino di Livello 3 o inferiore possono attaccare direttamente. Se questa carta viene mandata al Cimitero per attivare l'effetto di un mostro ACQUA: aggiungi 1 mostro Serpente Marino, eccetto \"Dragoni Atlantici\", dal tuo Deck alla tua mano."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Soldados de Cavalaria Atlante",
      "effect": "Todos os seus monstros Serpente Marinha de N\u00edvel 3 ou menos podem atacar diretamente. Se este card for enviado para o Cemit\u00e9rio para ativar o efeito de um monstro de \u00c1GUA: adicione 1 monstro Serpente Marinha do seu Deck \u00e0 sua m\u00e3o, exceto \"Soldados de Cavalaria Atlante\"."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Infantes Montados de Atlantis",
      "effect": "Todos tus monstruos Serpiente Marina de Nivel 3 o menor pueden atacar directamente. Si esta carta es mandada al Cementerio para activar el efecto de un monstruo de AGUA: a\u00f1ade a tu mano 1 monstruo Serpiente Marina en tu Deck, excepto \"Infantes Montados de Atlantis\"."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u6d77\u7687\u306e\u7adc\u9a0e\u968a",
      "effect": "\u2460\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u30be\u30fc\u30f3\u306b\u5b58\u5728\u3059\u308b\u9650\u308a\u3001\u81ea\u5206\u306e\u30ec\u30d9\u30eb\uff13\u4ee5\u4e0b\u306e\u6d77\u7adc\u65cf\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306f\u76f4\u63a5\u653b\u6483\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u2461\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u6c34\u5c5e\u6027\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u3092\u767a\u52d5\u3059\u308b\u305f\u3081\u306b\u5893\u5730\u3078\u9001\u3089\u308c\u305f\u5834\u5408\u306b\u767a\u52d5\u3059\u308b\u3002\u30c7\u30c3\u30ad\u304b\u3089\u300c\u6d77\u7687\u306e\u7adc\u9a0e\u968a\u300d\u4ee5\u5916\u306e\u6d77\u7adc\u65cf\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u624b\u672d\u306b\u52a0\u3048\u308b\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\ud574\ud669\uc758 \uc6a9\uae30\ub300",
      "effect": "\u2460: \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uac00 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130 \uc874\uc5d0 \uc874\uc7ac\ud558\ub294 \ud55c, \uc790\uc2e0\uc758 \ub808\ubca8 3 \uc774\ud558\uc758 \ud574\ub8e1\uc871 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\ub294 \uc9c1\uc811 \uacf5\uaca9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4. \u2461: \uc774 \uce74\ub4dc\uac00 \ubb3c \uc18d\uc131 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\uc758 \ud6a8\uacfc\ub97c \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud558\uae30 \uc704\ud574 \ubb18\uc9c0\ub85c \ubcf4\ub0b4\uc84c\uc744 \uacbd\uc6b0\uc5d0 \ubc1c\ub3d9\ud55c\ub2e4. \ub371\uc5d0\uc11c \"\ud574\ud669\uc758 \uc6a9\uae30\ub300\" \uc774\uc678\uc758 \ud574\ub8e1\uc871 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130 1\uc7a5\uc744 \ud328\uc5d0 \ub123\ub294\ub2e4."
    },
    "zh-TW": {
